They were commissioned by Olympia Trust Company to create their new boardroom table. 
They selected an irregular 16’ slab of claro walnut that normally would be unusable for a table this size. 
In order to make the piece functional we cast it in 270L of our Deep Resin. We tinted the resin with black liquid dye to provide a nice contrast with the walnut. 
In order to get the piece up 22 floors, the built it in two pieces and took it up through the elevator!
.
.
.
.
.
